The Fund shall be administered by the Minister who may—
(a) subject to section seven, invest any moneys for the time being standing to the credit of the Fund by way of deposit with banks or building societies or in Government Treasury Bills or in such stocks, shares, funds, securities or other investments or property as he may determine, with power to realise any moneys so invested and reinvest as aforesaid;
